4.7 stars A good setlist, with everything played at top form, and one of the best quaity AUDs I've ever heard, beating the sound of any other copy of this show to date, IMHO.
Clearinghouse of coincidences Went to High School with the girl in the Pic and was at this show.  Thanks for posting the link to those.  Very cool shots from the stage.
